org.modelio.vbasic.version

Class VersionedItem<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.modelio.vbasic.version.VersionedItem<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the attached data type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<VersionedItem<?>>

    public class VersionedItem<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<VersionedItem<?>>, java.io.Serializable
    Represents a versioned item.

    It is composed of a name identifying it and a version. Only these fields are used for equality and comparisons.

    The represented object or any other data may be attached by the setObject(Object) relation.

    Author:
    cmarin
